nit: since null doesn't have a special meaning internally you can avoid double null check on every addIfAbsent and do one of the null checks here:
this.connectionObserverFactory = connectionObserverFactory == null ? () -> null : connectionObserverFactory;
which could simplify the usage in addIfAbsent to:
final ConnectionObserver observer = connectionObserverFactory.get();

